text: Pseudobagrus omeihensis is a species of fish classified into the family Bagridae, included at order Siluriformes. ==Distribution== The fish lives in the region of O-mei Hsien, China.http://www.fishbase.se/summary/Pseudobagrus- omeihensis.html ==References== ==Bibliography== * Eschmeyer, William N., ed. 1998.
